  Locus:
    Page: 115
    Verse: 13
Tags:
  - Ego/Vanity
---
When you are governed by your ego, you are selfish and materialistic, but
insofar as you follow the promptings of your higher self, you will see
things realistically and find harmony within yourself and others.
